                        <interp inst="t18320705-106-victim959" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , on the 30th of June, and stealing 1 telescope, value 25s., and two pairs of shoes, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320705-106-victim961" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Gibson
                        <interp inst="t18320705-106-victim961" type="surname" value="Gibson"></interp>
